Developer Terms of Use
des:
Are you interested in Fresno/Clovis events, community, and real estate? The "FresYes Skill" has you covered. Brought to you by FresYes Realty | FresYes.com.

You can ask for our weekly community challenge, our weekly real estate highlight or our weekend events calendar. 

• Alexa ask FresYes for the weekend events
• Alexa, ask FresYes for the weekly community challenge
• Alexa ask FresYes for the weekly real estate highlight

You can easily navigate between content by saying next, previous or skip.

If you forget any of the FresYes skill's abilities just ask Alexa for "help"

Have questions or looking for more information? Email: marketing@fresyes.com
